## Metrics & Monitoring

Track policy engine decisions:

```python
metrics = engine.get_metrics()
# Returns:
# {
#   'total_decisions': 42,
#   'policy_counters': {'resource_optimization': 20, ...},
#   'status_counters': {'allowed': 35, 'denied': 7},
#   'avg_execution_time_ms': 2.3
# }
```

